==Korean==
===Verb===
'''[[그릇]][[되다]]''' geureut-doeda
#to be [[wrong]] (immoral); to be [[false]];  to be bad (a bad action, habit)
#:Note: literally means "to ''become'' wrong/false/bad" but will usually be translated with "be".
#:Example: 남을 속이는 일은 그릇된 짓이다. (''nameul sogineun ireun '''geureut-doein''' jis-ida). Deceiving people is '''wrong'''.

